text: Sandra Schilling (born 26 June 1989) is a German water polo player. She was part of the German women's national water polo team in the 2009 World Aquatics Championships, and 2009 FINA Women's Water Polo World League. == References == ==Other websites== * Women's WP World League (Bochum, Day 2): Greece loses first game, but is already in the Super Final | fina.org - Official FINA website. www.fina.org category:1989 births Category:Living people category:German water polo players
